<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Trump Wants to End Regulation That Cut Mercury Pollution by 81 Percent</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
<noscript><img width="1200" height="800" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury-1200x800.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="Coal-fired Bruce Mansfield Power Plant viewed from front porch of home." itemprop="url" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury-200x133.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury-400x267.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury-800x533.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"></noscript><img width="1200" height="800" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%203%202'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="Coal-fired Bruce Mansfield Power Plant viewed from front porch of home." itemprop="url" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury-200x133.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury-400x267.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury-800x533.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury.jpg 2400w" data-src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2019_0416-coal-mercury-1200x800.jpg" loading="lazy">
<figcaption class="wp-caption-text" itemprop="caption">Coal-related mercury pollution from power plants such as the one pictured here in Shippingport, Pennsylvania, has so contaminated the state's landscape that pregnant women are advised to limit local fish consumption to one meal per week.</figcaption><figcaption class="wp-caption-credit" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Robert Nickelsberg / Getty Images</span></figcaption></figure></div>
