</article>
<article class="reading-list-item">
<div class='sections' style='color: #2c5b53;'>Economy &amp; Labor</div>
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/covid-19-exposes-the-delicate-economic-balance-we-all-live-in-under-capitalism/">COVID-19 Exposes the Delicate Economic Balance We All Live in Under Capitalism</a>
</article>
<article class="reading-list-item">
<div class='sections' style='color: #2c5b53;'>Economy &amp; Labor</div>
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/ilhan-omar-bill-would-cancel-rent-and-mortgage-payments-for-duration-of-pandemic/">Ilhan Omar Bill Would Cancel Rent and Mortgage Payments for Duration of Pandemic</a>
</article>
<article class="reading-list-item">
<div class='sections' style='color: #1958aa;'>Politics &amp; Elections</div>
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/attorney-general-barr-refuses-to-release-9-11-documents-to-victims-families/">Attorney General Barr Refuses to Release 9/11 Documents to Victims&#8217; Families</a>
</article>
<article class="reading-list-item">
<div class='sections' style='color: #2c5b53;'>Economy &amp; Labor</div>
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/postal-workers-union-leader-warns-the-usps-could-be-dead-in-three-months/">Postal Workers Union Leader Warns the USPS Could Be Dead in Three Months</a>
</article>
</div>
</aside>
</div>
<div class="entry-content primary-content-column columns small-12 medium-8">
<p>Americans have one day left to tell the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) to preserve life-saving pollution standards.</p>
<p>Last year, the Trump administration proposed a plan to move forward with dismantling safeguards on dangerous mercury and toxic pollution from power plants. Doing so would boost levels of mercury, soot and other hazardous pollution into our nation&rsquo;s air, water, food and communities. These standards &mdash; the <a href="https://www.epa.gov/mats">Mercury and Air Toxics Standards (MATS)</a> &mdash; were developed in consultation with medical and public health experts in order to keep Americans healthy and safe.</p>
<p>As a doctor in Pennsylvania, I have seen just how important these standards are. Children are especially vulnerable to mercury&rsquo;s harmful effects on the brain before birth and during early childhood. Coal-related mercury pollution has so contaminated Pennsylvania&rsquo;s landscape that the state&rsquo;s Fish and Boat Commission has <a href="https://www.dep.pa.gov/Business/Water/CleanWater/WaterQuality/FishConsumptionAdvisory/Pages/default.aspx">advised</a> pregnant women to limit local fish consumption to one meal per week.</p><div class="truth-post-content-high  inline-callout-container" id="truth-255792"><aside class=" callout inline-callout callout--subscribe callout--dark" id="truth-255394">
<h2>Stay in the loop</h2>
<p>Never miss the news and analysis you care about.</p>
